## Version History
- v1.0 (Sprint 2) - Initial release with core features:
  - User authentication (Login/Register)
  - Add Consultation with crop recommendations
  - My Consultations with search, edit, delete
  - My Crops with growth tracking
  - Compare crops feature
  - Admin panel for crop and user management
  - Responsive design for mobile devices

